<!doctype html><html lang="ko"><head><% const brand=settings?.brand||{name:'서비스 디렉터리',showLogo:false,showName:true,logo:'',link:'/'}; %><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>글쓰기 - <%=board.title%></title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css"></head><body><header class="top"><a class="brand" href="/">홈</a><a class="site-brand-center" href="<%=brand.link||'/'%>"><% if(brand.showLogo&&brand.logo){%><img src="<%=brand.logo%>" alt=""><%}%><% if(brand.showName){%><span><%=brand.name%></span><%}%></a><nav><a href="/boards/<%=board.slug%>"><%=board.title%></a></nav></header><main class="board-wrap"><section class="board-top-banner"><b>커뮤니티 게시판</b><span>회원들과 정보를 나누고 소통하세요.</span></section><div class="board-head"><div><h1><%=board.title%> 글쓰기</h1><p><%=board.description||''%></p></div></div><% if(error){%><div class="board-form-error"><%=error%></div><%}%><form class="board-form" method="post" action="/boards/<%=board.slug%>/write" enctype="multipart/form-data"><label>제목<input name="title" minlength="2" maxlength="100" required></label><label>내용<textarea name="content" minlength="2" maxlength="5000" required></textarea></label><% if(board.image_enabled){%><label>이미지<input type="file" name="image" accept="image/jpeg,image/png,image/gif,image/webp"></label><div class="board-image-preview"><img alt="이미지 미리보기"></div><%}%><div class="board-actions"><a href="/boards/<%=board.slug%>">취소</a><button class="board-write-btn">등록</button></div></form></main><script src="/public/js/app.js"></script></body></html>
